_sText:
This is the vmf for some cell shaded brushes I made using TopHATTwaffle's youtube tutorials and some of my own thinking. They would look very nice in GunGame and Death Match and Fight Yard maps. Thanks for viewing, please download and rate. Constructive critisizm if you think they are not done right please.

Shapes include : 64x64 Box.
                 32x32 Box.
                 Sphere.
                 48x48 Pyrimid.
      guess -->  16x72 Cylinder.

Enjoy.
